name: Xeno Tezors #04 - Mindflay
description: She is a crossbreed between human and a gene compatible alien race created in laboratory.  For more than 20 years she was working for the intergalactic association to infiltrate the minds of criminals. Since the lichworm plague became a menace to all known worlds she plays a big role as a supporter in the army. She manipulates the soldiers minds in a way that they become fearless and bloodthirsty war machines.
